INSERT INTO `xrpk2_content` VALUES (1,54,'HOME','home-en','<p class=\"home\">Coloured, perfumed, tasty aromatic herbs the plants offer us a rich garden of emotions !</p>\r\n','',1,8,'2013-11-21 22:13:31',591,'','2013-11-29 14:33:56',591,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-11-21 22:13:31','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"0\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"0\",\"show_print_icon\":\"0\",\"show_email_icon\":\"0\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}',11,7,'','',1,349,'{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0,'en-GB',''),(2,55,'COMPANY','company-en','<p>Lorenzetto is based in Albenga in the Northern part of Italy, by the Ligurian Riviera. Since the 70s it produces and sells different kind of plants typical from the Albenga area.Lorenzetto is now one of the most reputable suppliers of potted Mediterranean plants and aromatics herbs in Italy.\r\nLorenzetto has 4 hectares of nurseries dedicated to growing plants such as herbs and other plants as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Moreover, it collaborates with more than 600 growers all over the area to be able to supply its customers a wide assortment of plants, ranging from aromatic herbs (such as lavender and rosemary) to daisies, euryops, felicia, gazania, osteospermum, lantana, solanum and many others.\r\nHowever, in the nurseries there are plants coming from the most important Italian production sites as well, whose incredible quality and variety is sought after in the whole of Europe.</p>\r\n\r\n','\r\n<p>\r\nIn particular, Lorenzetto can offer a wide range of Sicilian plants grown in the area of Messina such as olive trees, oleander, citrus, bouganville, palm trees.\r\nTogether with its partners in Sicily, it is possible to process and package the orders on the spot, to deliver them to its customers straight out from the production site.\r\nLorenzetto can provide plants from Tuscany as well such as buxus and cupressus and from the Lake Maggiore in the North of Italy, such as camelia, azalea and Rhododendron.\r\nDifferent plants are delivered according to the period of the year.\r\n \r\nDuring the fall manily herbs and plants such as Cyclamens and Chrysanthemums are sold. In the spring time Lorenzetto mainly supplies daisies (both bushes and standards) and the whole range of flowering plants from Albenga and other parts of Italy.\r\nLorenzetto is organised in a way to process the orders in the most efficient and quick manner. Once the order is placed the staff organize the logistic to deliver the plants as soon as possible. Besides Italian the employees speak German, Dutch, English and French.\r\nLorenzetto has a wide warehouse to process and package the orders on trolleys in the most efficient way.\r\n \r\nThe plants are then delivered with the most reliable European companies using refrigerated trucks.\r\nLorenzettos customers are wholesales, garden centre and distributors all over Europe. Lorenzetto can provide lost of different services such as: pre-pricing on the pots, special packaging, customised mixed trolleys.\r\n \r\nDuring the high season a large number of plants are delivered everyday in Germany, Austria, Switzerland, France, Holland, Belgium, UK, Check republic, Denmark , Poland and Italy as well.\r\nLorenzetto is known for the optimal aspect and characteristics of the plants and for the very good quality-price ratio. These are the reasons why Lorenzetto has become today a leading exporting producer on both local and international markets, offering quality products together with an efficient and reliable service.\r\n</p> ',1,17,'2013-11-21 22:13:47',591,'','2013-12-28 11:26:47',591,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-11-21 22:13:47','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}',10,6,'','',1,112,'{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0,'en-GB',''),(3,56,'PRODUCTS','products-en','<p>In this section you can find the main plants marketed by the company Lorenzetto.\r\nLeafing through the catalogue Lorenzetto, you will have the full range of the products