iversit\\u00e0, non fa uso di input chimici ed \\u00e8 certificata no OGM in tutta la filiera.\\r\\nMantiene la produzione nel tempo, conservando o aumentando la fertilit\\u00e0 del terreno; crea una minor dipendenza dagli input esterni e favorisce la filiera corta.\\r\\nPer garantire questa tipologia di prodotto offriamo ai nostri clienti anche una linea di piante aromatiche biologiche nel vaso \\u00d812.\\r\\nLe nostre aromatiche biologiche sono un prodotto  di alta qualit\\u00e0 e lunga durata, risultato di un rigoroso metodo di coltivazione.\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n{gallery}aromi-bio{\\/gallery}\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"11\",\"created\":\"2013-12-08 21:27:35\",\"created_by\":\"591\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2013-12-28 09:43:20\",\"modified_by\":\"591\",\"checked_out\":\"591\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2013-12-28 09:42:24\",\"publish_up\":\"2013-12-08 21:27:35\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_pr